Welcome to Ubuntu 18.04.3 LTS (GNU/Linux 4.15.0-66-generic x86_64)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At the server:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;console&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;~ vi ~/.bashrc&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Press ‘i’ for insert,
Esc -&gt; :w -&gt; Save the file.
Esc -&gt; :q -&gt; Quit the Vi Editor&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Copy the below line and add it at the end of &lt;em&gt;.bashrc&lt;/em&gt; file:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token assign-left variable&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token environment constant&quot;&gt;PS1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token operator&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;token string&quot;&gt;&apos;\[\033[1;36m\]\u\[\033[1;31m\]@\[\033[1;32m\]\h:\[\033[1;35m\]\w\[\033[1;31m\]\$\[\033[0m\] &apos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exit &amp;#x26; Login again to see the effect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;console&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;~ exit&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;console&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;~ ssh root@165.227.194.244&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Step 3 Install Apache&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If this step you got error, you can read at &lt;a href=&quot;https://vitux.com/how-to-install-and-configure-apache-web-server-on-ubuntu/&quot;&gt;More detail&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;~ sudo apt update
~ sudo apt install apache2&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check the version&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;console&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;~ apache2 -version&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check status of Apache&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;console&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-console&quot;&gt;~ sudo systemctl status apache2&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Check IP&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;text&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;~ hostname -I&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
